versity of pennsylvania qualifications mr hassenfeld has an extensive and broad background in business management including his experience as a chief executive officer of a publicly traded company this deep business knowledge combined with the leadership roles he plays within many philanthropic organizations supports our conclusion that mr hassenfeld has the necessary and desired skills experience and perspective to serve on our board source salesforce on    sign up for equilar atlas and view alan g hassenfelds full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like alan g hassenfeld more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in alan g hassenfelds network and community follow changes in alan g hassenfelds employment and moneyinmotion connect with alan g hassenfeld through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example alan g hassenfeld alan g hassenfelds connections  sign up now to view alan g hassenfelds  connections » rochelle b lazarus board member general electric company tracy a leinbach board member hasbro inc edward b rust board member sp global inc michael i roth chairman of the board and chief executive officer the interpublic group of companies inc barry salzberg former board member thomson reuters corporation henrietta h fore board member exxon mobil corporation marc benioff chairman of the board and chief executive officer salesforce richard j harrington former consulting advisor and former chief executive officer thomson reuters corporation maynard g webb board member salesforce claudine b malone former board member novell popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith carl g annessa evp and coo hornbeck offshore services inc elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla michael c montgomery board member nmi holdings inc × c